  "body": "Deposits have a couple of problems:\n\n- The state we generate using Deposits and PoW Chain Service does not get set as ChainStorageClient's Store's genesis State, and thus, we actually discard it.\n\n- Validator Coordinator adds pre-genesis Deposits to its blocks (because it is subscribed to any kind of deposit on the event bus) these deposits should actually only be processed before the genesis state, and not be included after genesis.\n \n- Validator Coordinator never cleans out old deposits from its newDeposits list, redundantly adding old deposits every time it's proposing a new block. \n",
